As regards the therapeutic effect of 15 Lys-bis-Nt and Lys-bis-Nt on HSV1-infected BALB/c mice, 15Lys-bis-Nt (30mg/kgwt) injected intraperitoneally two times a day for 5 days (the first dose was administered 2 h after the infection) reduced mortality by 45% (cf 60% in the control group (infected but untreated mice) (
 Andronova et al., 2012; 
 Andronova, Grokhovsky, Surovaya, Gursky, & Galegov, 2013).
